attributes.Long form description: The student is disassembling a table. They unscrew the screws on the legs, then rotate the table and unscrew the screws on the shelves. They set the hex socket heads aside, then grabbed a hex socket head and an allen wrench. They disassembled the top shelf of the table and set it aside. Then they do the same for the bottom shelf. Finally, they turn the table around and disassemble the legs of the bottom shelf.
